Adam,

I hope all is well. I wanted to reach out regarding the subscription docume=
nts for the investment in Vestar VII. It looks like we are all sorted out a=
nd there is no need to fill out the additional documentation as long as the=
re is proof of residence in Israel. Accordingly, some adjustments will need=
 to be made to the subscription document to reflect this. I have outlined t=
his below:

-          Domicile in the subscription booklet must reflect Israel, not UK=
 - please revise Part IV(f) and (g) of the IQS to reflect the residence in =
Israel

-          Please provide a revised Self-Certification form, W-8BEN, AML pr=
oof of address and notice address

Please do not hesitate to reach out if you have any questions.

Best,
Ariana

